window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Leila Rajput is a young girl, struggling with life and relationships, dealing with the trauma of a past life event. Unaware of her true potential, she has almost given up on life, till she meets the dynamic, near-perfect Vikrant Rao via the internet. He identifies her potential and offers her a strange arrangement - to be her mentor. He teaches her the basics of life, makes her realize her dreams and helps her in achieving them step by step. Under his guidance, she evolves into a confident and independent woman. They eventually fall in love, and Vikrant relocates to her city, where he meets her friend Maya. While he solves Maya's life conflicts and helps her elope with Shahan, he charges a fee none could ever imagine. </p> <p>Is Vikrant a villain or a victim of greed? Did he truly love Leila, or was she just a puppet to reach his next victim? </p> <p><i>Was It Love?</i> is a story of Leila's journey through emotions, trials, betrayal and the devil called love.</p>"; 
